{"tid":1822964,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個大陸仔特徵","createTime":"2020-01-13T09:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T03:31:22.000Z","uid":259724,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"1267b4122ca0bda09f7e4d9535117f68bb79c9c7","tid":1822964,"uid":259724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:47:31.000Z","msg":"前排搭飛機返嚟香港，隔離坐左個大陸仔，先發覺大陸仔好易認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 傾都唔撚想同佢傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想問下連登仔眼中有咩大陸仔特徵<br />\n<br />\n最撚易認:<br />\n<br />\n口音:妖 大陸口音邊撚似香港啊 dllm <br />\n香港人得一個口音 就係香港口音 <br />\n咪撚咁比較 完<br />\n「你是咪來自Xiang gang」 「禾好喜欢香港」「香港口音姣似廣州口音」<br />\n屌你 咁你彈撚返大陸啦 香港不是你家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n髮型:典型大陸仔髮型<br />\n平頭 大陸味極濃 勁嘔心<br />\n不了<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢睇我有連登 問「nei有玩連登?禾都知」<br />\n關你乜撚事 又係想扮香港人<br />\n<br />\n之後睇到佢部手機，望都唔使再望就知係大陸仔<br />\n用WeChat殘體字同大陸妹傾，song playlist全部大陸歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得少廣東歌<br />\n<br />\n屌 之後估你唔撚到<br />\n睇香港電影！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知係咪咁撚鐘意香港定大陸冇播香港電影<br />\n可能真係想扮係香港人<br />\n佢地好撚鐘意睇咩監獄片 古惑仔個d<br />\n全程都睇呢d片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後 佢問我 「加我微信」<br />\n屌你 乜撚啊 睬都唔睬就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a796a3fb4b21ccd0200bacfa8a52040157eb99","tid":1822964,"uid":143367,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:48:21.000Z","msg":"女人就圓框眼鏡"},{"pid":"c092a48e3e943b381cee6d879e77853b6488d9a7","tid":1822964,"uid":152455,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:48:56.000Z","msg":"樣7、牛屎佬、全身男有7味，女有雞格"},{"pid":"624f3dc6b9d